{"tid":2492533,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"譚仔上市；我又搞搞新意思!","createTime":"2021-04-17T07:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-28T23:17:36.000Z","uid":246729,"like":80,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4a443dea4caef7a1ae74f3ed447eed9d8b4d1f","tid":2492533,"uid":246729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:35:38.000Z","msg":"譚仔上市；我又搞搞新意思！拍片講！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TPzL4TBi_7M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTPzL4TBi_7M&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=71a4f85d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TPzL4TBi_7M</a><br />\n睇佢數簿！譚仔上市啦！毛利率高？同業比較？租金只佔2％？增長面？風險因素？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WOA9GQjh8qtn2T6V8KorlD4awlB6fyBv/view?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1WOA9GQjh8qtn2T6V8KorlD4awlB6fyBv%2Fview%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CLxyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=4e558806\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WOA9GQjh8qtn2T6V8KorlD4awlB6fyBv/view?usp=sharing</a><br />\n片入面嘅PPT<br />\n<br />\n我平時如果要寫一篇認真嘅分析， 或者就咁打一篇Blog 都大約要大半日<br />\n首要係本身我成日坐唔定<br />\n而且念頭太多， 打字太慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嘗試過搵語音輸音， 效果一般<br />\n<br />\n一路都想試一路影住個screen ， 我一路講<br />\n好似online補習咁，分享比大家我睇年報/招股書 嘅流程<br />\n<br />\n但又怕會悶親大家<br />\n今次試下cap圖放重點落PPT咁， 我嚟present<br />\n<br />\n今次試完感覺幾好<br />\n起碼無打字咁攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加上懶人嘅方法， 1take 唔剪接<br />\n<br />\n唔知咁多位讀者/網友 有無咩feedback？<br />\n<br />\n希望大家盡情比feedback<br />\n<br />\n我嘅最終目標： 可以喺Youtube 夠人數訂閱，定期做下Live<br />\n可以即時同你地交流<br />\n一問一答； 快問快答<br />\n<br />\n平時睇News好多意念不斷走出嚟， 但都太懶打字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2cac4e0626e7b22d43c45405fb99d6b423c06b6","tid":2492533,"uid":249207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:36:16.000Z","msg":"支持